{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"a83ea9ad-fe41-4941-897f-7458504847f3","content":"Here's the plan and architecture for your RAG-based Q&A feature:\n\n---\n\n## Architecture Overview\n\n```\n┌──────────────┐      ┌──────────────────┐      ┌────────────────┐\n│  Docs/*.md   │─────▶│  Ingestion       │─────▶│  Vector Store  │\n│  (source)    │      │  (chunk+embed)   │      │  (in-memory or │\n└──────────────┘      └──────────────────┘      │   persistent)  │\n                                                 └───────┬────────┘\n                                                         │\n┌──────────────┐      ┌──────────────────┐               │\n│  User Query  │─────▶│  POST /ask       │──── search ───┘\n│              │      │  (embed+retrieve │\n└──────────────┘      │   +generate)     │──── top-K chunks ──▶ LLM ──▶ Answer\n                      └──────────────────┘\n```\n\n---\n\n## Key Components\n\n| Layer | Responsibility | Suggested Package |\n|-------|---------------|-------------------|\n| **Chunking** | Split markdown by headings/paragraphs into ~300-500 token chunks with overlap | `Microsoft.Extensions.AI` or custom splitter |\n| **Embedding** | Convert chunks → vectors | `Microsoft.Extensions.AI` (OpenAI / Azure OpenAI embeddings) |\n| **Vector Store** | Store & similarity-search embeddings | `Microsoft.Extensions.VectorData` + in-memory provider (swap for Qdrant/Azure AI Search later) |\n| **Retrieval** | Embed query → find top-K similar chunks | Cosine similarity via vector store |\n| **Generation** | Send top-K chunks + question to LLM | `Microsoft.Extensions.AI` chat completion |\n\n---\n\n## Endpoints\n\n| Method | Route | Purpose |\n|--------|-------|---------|\n| `POST` | `/ingest` | Read all `Docs/*.md`, chunk, embed, store vectors. Returns chunk count. |\n| `POST` | `/ask` | Accept `{ \"question\": \"...\" }`, retrieve relevant chunks, call LLM, return grounded answer + source references. |\n\n---\n\n## Ingestion Pipeline\n\n1. Enumerate `Docs/*.md` files\n2. For each file: split into chunks (heading-aware, ~400 tokens, 50-token overlap)\n3. Generate embeddings for each chunk (batch call)\n4. Store in vector store with metadata (filename, heading, position)\n\n## Query Pipeline\n\n1. Embed the user's question\n2. Vector similarity search → top 3–5 chunks\n3. Build a system prompt: *\"Answer using only the provided context\"*\n4. Call chat completion with context + question\n5. Return answer + source chunk references\n\n---\n\n## NuGet Packages to Add\n\n- `Microsoft.Extensions.AI.OpenAI` — unified AI abstractions (embeddings + chat)\n- `Microsoft.Extensions.VectorData.Abstractions` — vector store abstraction\n- `Microsoft.Extensions.VectorData.InMemory` — zero-infrastructure dev store\n\n---\n\n## Considerations\n\n- **No external infra needed for dev** — in-memory vector store works out of the box; swap to a persistent store for production.\n- **Chunking strategy** — markdown heading boundaries preserve semantic coherence; overlap prevents lost context at boundaries.\n- **Grounding** — the system prompt constrains the LLM to only use retrieved content, reducing hallucination.\n- **Incremental ingestion** — for a production version, hash files and skip unchanged ones.\n\nWant me to implement this?","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"fe91aa8b-d1a7-4d89-b554-ed37323f8fcb","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"Now I have a good understanding of the current state. Let me create a plan for the RAG-based Q&A feature. The user explicitly said \"do not write any code\" and wants plan and architecture only.\n\nLet me create a comprehensive plan.","outputTokens":954,"requestId":"C01B:2CA3BD:2017E7C:244EDB4:6A07D49A"},"id":"f919e9be-fa6e-4c55-8423-4f6eb098e216","timestamp":"2026-05-16T02:21:33.010Z","parentId":"02483a15-d2c6-4d86-9063-0bdff2fd3b72"}
